pin-media=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/GScHw42jwEdp2eq8WSfoeH.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/picture\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003e(Image credit: Future/Ninja)\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003eWhat about the Ninja Slushi, I hear you ask? Sold out via Ninja, the Slushi is the hype kitchen appliance of this year.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eLuckily, I\u0026#39;ve found the one place it\u0026#39;s in stock: on Amazon, though you will pay an extra £76.72 in shipping fees on top of the RRP if you go down this route. But if you just can\u0026#39;t wait to make slushies at home, this is your best bet.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eNinja Slushi | \u003c/strong\u003e\u003ca data-analytics-id=\"inline-link\" href=\"https://www.amazon.co.uk/Ninja-FS301-Professional-RapidChill-Technology/dp/B0D2LZYQ2M/ref=sr_1_4\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e£376.72 at Amazon\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ctime datetime=\"2024-11-26T10:07:29+00:00\"\u003e2024-11-26T10:07:29.810Z\u003c/time\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure data-bordeaux-image-check=\"\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cpicture\u003e\u003csource type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/kWHMuyKFi6fxYm4Fnrcc7Q-1920-80.jpg.webp 1920w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/kWHMuyKFi6fxYm4Fnrcc7Q-1600-80.jpg.webp 1600w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/kWHMuyKFi6fxYm4Fnrcc7Q-1280-80.jpg.webp 1280w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/kWHMuyKFi6fxYm4Fnrcc7Q-1024-80.jpg.webp 1024w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/kWHMuyKFi6fxYm4Fnrcc7Q-768-80.jpg.webp 768w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/kWHMuyKFi6fxYm4Fnrcc7Q-415-80.jpg.webp 415w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/kWHMuyKFi6fxYm4Fnrcc7Q-360-80.jpg.webp 360w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/kWHMuyKFi6fxYm4Fnrcc7Q-320-80.jpg.webp 320w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 710px) 670px, calc(100vw - 30px)\"/\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/kWHMuyKFi6fxYm4Fnrcc7Q-320-80.jpg\" alt=\"Currys White air fryer deal\" srcset=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/kWHMuyKFi6fxYm4Fnrcc7Q-1920-80.jpg 1920w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/kWHMuyKFi6fxYm4Fnrcc7Q-1600-80.jpg 1600w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/kWHMuyKFi6fxYm4Fnrcc7Q-1280-80.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/kWHMuyKFi6fxYm4Fnrcc7Q-1024-80.jpg 1024w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/kWHMuyKFi6fxYm4Fnrcc7Q-768-80.jpg 768w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/kWHMuyKFi6fxYm4Fnrcc7Q-415-80.jpg 415w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/kWHMuyKFi6fxYm4Fnrcc7Q-360-80.jpg 360w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/kWHMuyKFi6fxYm4Fnrcc7Q-320-80.jpg 320w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 710px) 670px, calc(100vw - 30px)\" loading=\"lazy\" data-original-mos=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/kWHMuyKFi6fxYm4Fnrcc7Q.jpg\" data-pin-media=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/kWHMuyKFi6fxYm4Fnrcc7Q.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/picture\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003e(Image credit: Future/Currys)\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003eEven though I\u0026#39;m an obvious air fryer convert, I\u0026#39;m the first person to agree that these appliances could be a lot prettier.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eThat\u0026#39;s why I\u0026#39;m a big fan of the Currys white Ninja air fryer range, which features the Dual Zone and the Double Stack. I roped in \u003cem\u003eIdeal Home\u0026#39;s \u003c/em\u003eContent Editor \u003ca data-analytics-id=\"inline-link\" href=\"https://www.idealhome.co.uk/author/holly-cockburn\" data-before-rewrite-localise=\"https://www.idealhome.co.uk/author/holly-cockburn\"\u003eHolly Cockburn\u003c/a\u003e to weigh in with her opinion on picking up an air fryer in the white colourway.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u0026#39;Not only is this air fryer actually super chic,\u0026#39; says Holly, \u0026#39;but it will also look far better alongside cream (or even pink) small appliances if black isn\u0026#39;t your thing. I\u0026#39;m dreaming of it sitting atop a marble-effect worktop in a navy or light grey kitchen - it will complete the look.\u0026#39;\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eCatch them on sale if you like the look too.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eNINJA Foodi MAX Dual Zone in White | \u003c/strong\u003e\u003ca data-analytics-id=\"inline-link\" href=\"https://www.currys.co.uk/products/ninja-foodi-max-dual-zone-af400ukwh-air-fryer-white-10256363.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"\u003e\u003cdel\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e£229.00\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/del\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e, now £169.99 at Currys\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eNinja Double Stack XL 2 Drawer Air Fryer 9.5L | \u003c/strong\u003e\u003ca data-analytics-id=\"inline-link\" href=\"https://www.currys.co.uk/products/ninja-double-stack-xl-sl400ukwh-air-fryer-white-10269802.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"\u003e\u003cdel\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eWas £269.99\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/del\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e, now £219.00 at Currys\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ctime datetime=\"2024-11-26T09:38:09+00:00\"\u003e2024-11-26T09:38:09.333Z\u003c/time\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure data-bordeaux-image-check=\"\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cpicture\u003e\u003csource type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/gmnsuhKHCxaxk7HZ4rNWXJ-1920-80.jpg.webp 1920w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/gmnsuhKHCxaxk7HZ4rNWXJ-1600-80.jpg.webp 1600w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/gmnsuhKHCxaxk7HZ4rNWXJ-1280-80.jpg.webp 1280w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/gmnsuhKHCxaxk7HZ4rNWXJ-1024-80.jpg.webp 1024w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/gmnsuhKHCxaxk7HZ4rNWXJ-768-80.jpg.webp 768w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/gmnsuhKHCxaxk7HZ4rNWXJ-415-80.jpg.webp 415w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/gmnsuhKHCxaxk7HZ4rNWXJ-360-80.jpg.webp 360w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.ne