rong\u003e. It\u0026#39;s got the versatility for family cooking. If you need to use 2 drawers to cater to different dinner preferences, you can just pop the divider in. \u003cstrong\u003e3. \u003c/strong\u003eIt\u0026#39;s supremely powerful, and can cook oven chips in silly-quick time.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eNinja Foodi FlexDrawer | \u003c/strong\u003e\u003ca data-analytics-id=\"inline-link\" href=\"https://www.amazon.co.uk/Ninja-FlexDrawer-Removable-Dishwasher-AF500UKCP/dp/B0CJ3CFJVT/ref=asc_df_B0CJ3CFJVT\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"\u003e\u003cdel\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e£269.99\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/del\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e, now £199.99 at Amazon\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ctime datetime=\"2024-11-26T09:19:49+00:00\"\u003e2024-11-26T09:19:49.409Z\u003c/time\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure data-bordeaux-image-check=\"\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cpicture\u003e\u003csource type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/wQfqTcDVSidKtBEwNPEYYj-1920-80.jpg.webp 1920w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/wQfqTcDVSidKtBEwNPEYYj-1600-80.jpg.webp 1600w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/wQfqTcDVSidKtBEwNPEYYj-1280-80.jpg.webp 1280w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/wQfqTcDVSidKtBEwNPEYYj-1024-80.jpg.webp 1024w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/wQfqTcDVSidKtBEwNPEYYj-768-80.jpg.webp 768w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/wQfqTcDVSidKtBEwNPEYYj-415-80.jpg.webp 415w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/wQfqTcDVSidKtBEwNPEYYj-360-80.jpg.webp 360w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/wQfqTcDVSidKtBEwNPEYYj-320-80.jpg.webp 320w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 710px) 670px, calc(100vw - 30px)\"/\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/wQfqTcDVSidKtBEwNPEYYj-320-80.jpg\" alt=\"pink certified expert appliances logo next to headshot of Molly Cleary\" srcset=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/wQfqTcDVSidKtBEwNPEYYj-1920-80.jpg 1920w, https://